  "content": {
    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following best explains why the polymerase from the species <span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic\">T. aquaticus </span>is often used for <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P C R\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"P C R\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><mtext>PCR</mtext></mrow></math></span></span>?</p>\n",
